1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,020
Four ways to get paid.

2
00:00:01,420 --> 00:00:02,120
One URL.

3
00:00:03,160 --> 00:00:04,960
The Stripe of USDC on Arc

4
00:00:04,960 --> 00:00:06,640
For humans and AI agents.

5
00:00:06,640 --> 00:00:07,600
Mode one. Tips.

6
00:00:07,600 --> 00:00:09,120
Every tweet gets a tip button.

7
00:00:09,120 --> 00:00:11,640
Chrome extension injects it next to reply and retweet.

8
00:00:12,160 --> 00:00:13,060
Mode two. Subscriptions.

9
00:00:13,240 --> 00:00:15,800
Like Substack, but creators keep 98%.

10
00:00:15,800 --> 00:00:17,200
Per-second accrual, prorated refunds.

11
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:18,120
Mode three. Content paywall.

12
00:00:18,120 --> 00:00:20,600
Gumroad with an on-chain receipt.

13
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:22,180
Pay once, own forever.

14
00:00:22,620 --> 00:00:23,460
Mode four. Pay-per-call.

15
00:00:23,460 --> 00:00:25,800
Prepay 100 inference credits in one transaction.

16
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:29,740
Every call after that is a wallet signature.

17
00:00:29,740 --> 00:00:30,880
x402, ERC-8183.

18
00:00:30,880 --> 00:00:31,620
2% protocol fee.

19
00:00:31,620 --> 00:00:36,920
0.5s settlement. Native USDC gas.

20
00:00:36,920 --> 00:00:39,440
Start building. npm create arc-app.
